    "summary": "Mijn missie: altijd kwalitatief goed bier uit de tap in heel Nederland. \n\nMy personal mission is to share the stories of great beer worldwide.  \n\nDriven by my passion for the craft-beer industry, in my beer career over the past 17 years I have been operational manager of the first Dutch Beer bar Arendsnest and the first American Beer bar in Europe the Beertemple location Amsterdam, The Netherlands. My responsibilities in these award winning bars were staff selection, inventory management, operational management, hosting fundraisers and beer tasting events.\n\nI recently graduated at Hotelschool The Hague and obtained the Bachelor Business Administration in Hotel Management (BBA.HM). During this International Fast Track Program at hotelschool The hague I excelled in annual budget analysis, brand development and rebranding projects.",
